{"tid":748302,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【封殺港獨】台灣陸委會回應民族黨 指港府應提供證據","createTime":"2018-07-19T06:09:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-19T07:00:47.000Z","uid":92301,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7d5aa56e2815bc3e88ee50fa19909f17b83c10b7","tid":748302,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T06:09:24.000Z","msg":"香港保安局局長李家超昨日（17日）指，當局首次引用《社團條例》，考慮禁止香港民族黨運作。台灣陸委會回應事件時，表示香港居民是享有言論、結社、集會等自由，並稱若港府認為香港民族黨「危害國家與公共安全或他人的權利和自由」，應盡快提出證據釐清真相。<br />\n<br />\n陸委會指出，根據香港《基本法》第27條，香港居民是享有言論、結社、集會等自由，認為港府應該盡快提出明確證據，才有助釐清真相和解除大眾的疑慮。陸委會並稱，將會持續密切關注事件發展。<br />\n<br />\n香港民族黨召集人陳浩天昨晚表示，估計因他本月1日曾到台灣主持一個記者會，現場有台灣政界人士，令當局「出手」禁止香港民族黨運作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180718/58456544\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180718%2F58456544&d=PmFcvYDdyGly%2FsMPmmCiDUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=1cf32777\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180718%2F58456544&h=49ffa9df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180718/58456544</a>"},{"pid":"22ee4106b0f7d5b490b3027a5ec467b9926d2da8","tid":748302,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T06:21:40.000Z","msg":"幾時修改港澳條例？"},{"pid":"3ee1f1a5d9d89283889ea4ba2ca5d25ee0a23f19","tid":748302,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T06:23:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0259624a5cc0b69a249927465ed56f77fffd1292","tid":748302,"uid":11962,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T06:24:21.000Z","msg":"一早無左法治好耐，有錢好快啲走"},{"pid":"179de68a524503adf7157804ffdc66d687c706d7","tid":748302,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T06:44:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"